    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade 997.2 Carrera S, featuring the robust 3.8L DFI flat-six engine\u2014a naturally aspirated masterpiece delivering 385 hp with linear precision. This example is equipped with the rare 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. The chassis is anchored by Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), ensuring exceptional damping response and lateral rigidity. Meticulously maintained, the vehicle exhibits zero bore scoring concerns inherent to earlier architectures, and the underside reveals a factory-clean transaxle and exhaust manifold. This is a concours-level specimen with verified paint depth and a comprehensive service dossier.",
